#: temp.glade:2615
msgid "This option creates a DIGLOT / POLYGLOT front matter\n"
"template designed for publications with two (or more)\n"
"languages or scripts. It is deliberately more complete\n"
"than the BASIC and ADVANCED templates because diglots\n"
"are inherently complex: two (or more) texts, often two\n"
"contents lists, two prefaces, sometimes two scripts and\n"
"two writing directions. Delete the sections you do not need.\n\n"
"Like the ADVANCED template it uses \\zvar|variables\\* and\n"
"\\zglot|L\\* / \\zglot|R\\* markers for column-specific content,\n"
"so it requires editing before use and is NOT suitable for\n"
"use inside Paratext without prior modification.\n\n"
"If this option is disabled, the Diglot setting is not\n"
"enabled for this configuration."
msgstr ""

